'''''Star Wars Insider'' 31''' is the thirty-first issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was published in Fall [[1996]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk" {{C|by [[Dan Madsen]]}}
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Prequel Update]]" {{C|by Dan Madsen with [[Rick McCallum]]}}
*"[[Star News]]"
*"[[The Wonder Column|The New Wonder Column]]" {{C|by [[Anthony Daniels]]}}
*"[[In the Star Wars Universe|The ''Star Wars'' Universe]]" &ndash; [[Michael Carter]]: Fortuna(te)? Son? {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*"[[The Jawa Trader|Jawa Trader]]"
*"[[The Horse's Mouth|Straight from the Horse's Mouth]]" {{C|by [[Bob Cooper]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet]]}}

===Features===
*"[[Pick a Card, Any Card: Making Movie Magic at Decipher, Inc.]]" {{C|by [[Jack Scrip]]}}
*:<small>Go inside the ''Star Wars'' Customizable Collectible Card Game with Jack Scrip</small>
*"[[Wicket Unleashed]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*:<small>Scott Chernoff interviews Warwick Davis, the man behind Wicket, Willow, and Leprechaun.</small>
*"[[Building a Better Jedi: Justin Chin on Dark Forces II|Building a Better Jedi: Justin Chin on ''Dark Forces II'']]" {{C|by [[Jon Bradley Snyder]]}}
*:<small>Jon Bradley Snyder finds out what's so cool about Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II, from LucasArts' Justin Chin.</small>
*"[[Star Wars Cinematographer: An Interview with Gil Taylor|''Star Wars'' Cinematographer: An Interview with Gil Taylor]]" {{C|by [[Jamie Painter]]}}
*:<small>Jamie Painter speaks with the world renowned cinematographer about shooting his most famous work.</small>
*"[[Kenner Is Cooking with Star Wars!|Kenner Is Cooking with ''Star Wars''!]]" {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet]]}}
*:<small>Stephen J. Sansweet reveals the secret Kenner action figure, and much more!</small>

